column11: We went to this beach as it had beautiful photos, but in reality the waves were so huge we couldn’t even enter the water. You can only take photos and that's all.
golden sandy beach, high waves for surfing, the long and wide beach for playing, restaurants are available on the beach.
Such a beautiful beach....clean, uncrowded, friendly but fun waves. Loved it! Some of our group took surfing lessons, some were able to body surfing & some just relaxed. Picturesque!

I came here with my wife who is leading a yoga retreat. This spot is great for that...3 studios all complete with props & a view of te ocean. We loved the service & food. Our room was quiet & cool. We’ll definitely be back & being our family!
